---
import { CATEGORIES } from '../lib/categories'

const legend = Object.values(CATEGORIES)
---

<footer class="text-center pt-12 pb-20 mt-8 border-t border-spine">
  <p class="font-sans text-xs leading-relaxed text-muted max-w-sm mx-auto mb-7">
    Every entry is checked against an authoritative source: the time-zone records kept
    by IANA, the leap seconds announced by IERS, and the standards written by the IETF.
  </p>

  <ul class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-x-4 gap-y-2 max-w-xs mx-auto">
    {legend.map((c) => (
      <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5 font-sans text-[11px] text-muted">
        <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full" style={`background:${c.node}`} aria-hidden="true"></span>
        {c.name}
      </li>
    ))}
  </ul>

  <p class="font-sans text-[11px] leading-relaxed text-muted mt-8 max-w-md mx-auto">
    Built with Opus and Sonnet, independently cross-checked with DeepSeek V4 and GPT-5.5 high
    across tens of millions of tokens, then verified against primary sources.
  </p>
  <p class="font-sans text-[11px] leading-relaxed text-muted mt-2 max-w-sm mx-auto">
    Found an error?
    <a class="text-link underline" href="https://github.com/yasinmiran/timeshift/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
      Open an issue <span aria-hidden="true">&#8599;</span><span class="sr-only"> (opens in a new tab)</span>
    </a>
  </p>
</footer>
